<h3 id="FpDykB"><strong>Like a Dragon: Infinite Wealth</strong></h3>
<div class="c-wide-block">  <figure class="e-image">
  <span class="e-image__inner">
    
    <span class="e-image__image " data-original="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25199704/bomy9fmo.png">
      
